Jade Osiberu’s ‘Brotherhood’ has won the ‘Best Movie West Africa award at the 2023 Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards. The movie stars top acts like Mercy Aigbe, Tobi Bakre, Boma Akpore, Falz, and Basketmouth, amongst others. Brotherhood beat the movies Choke, Anikulapo, Kanaani, Red Carpet, and Four Four Forty-Four to emerge the winner. Details later…